          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">thiol</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">group</ENAMEX> of a <NUMEX TYPE="ORDINAL">second</NUMEX> substrate. The bacterial GshBs
