          cyanophycin synthetases and <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">D</ENAMEX>-<ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Ala-D</ENAMEX>-<ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Ala</ENAMEX> ligases. Notably,
