          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">eukaryotes</ENAMEX>. For example, 
          A. thaliana has at least three
          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">superfamily</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">members</ENAMEX> in the PSI-BLAST output, including
          carbamoyl <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">phosphate synthetase</ENAMEX>, <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">3</NUMEX>-<NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">methylcrotonyl</NUMEX>-CoA
