          than to eukaryotic <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">GshBs</ENAMEX>.
          Crystal structures of <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">GshBs</ENAMEX> from 
          <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">E. coli</ENAMEX> [ <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">42</TIMEX>] and human [ <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">43</TIMEX>] are
